---
name: Jhancy Rani Avula
title: Deaconess — Women's & Children's Ministry
category: deaconess
order: 18
---

Jhancy Rani Avula leads the women's and children's ministry at Grace Life Church, Vizag. She is the wife of Pastor Daniel Surya Avula and a faithful servant of God, committed to equipping women and nurturing children in the faith.
